<div id='communityQuestionsWithAnswers'>
<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/901442-did-anyone-else-find-the-chronology">Did anyone else find the chronology confusing? Every chapter is dated and I thought I was following the back and forth through time correctly. But then I started having troubling figuring out the sequence of events. Maybe when I finish the book, I will understand better what the author was doing.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
