<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/3391581-tiffany-s">Tiffany S</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">YES!!! I think it would have helped if it identified the viewpoint the chapter was from as well. It would say the month and year but a few chapters to<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">YES!!! I think it would have helped if it identified the viewpoint the chapter was from as well. It would say the month and year but a few chapters took me at least a paragraph or two to go OOOH this is a Freddie chapter!<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
